    signal BOOT ~ pin 1
    signal VIN ~ pin 2
    signal EN ~ pin 3
    signal SS ~ pin 4
    signal VSENSE ~ pin 5
    signal COMP ~ pin 6
    signal GND ~ pin 7
    signal PH ~ pin 8
